By Brother Peter Dimond, O.S.B.
Source: vaticancatholic.com
OBJECTION- What about Invincible Ignorance?
ANSWER-&nbsp;
2 Corinthians 4:3: “And if our gospel be hid, it is hid to them that are lost, in whom the god of this world [Satan] hath blinded the minds of unbelievers, that the light of the gospel of the glory of Christ, who is the image of God, should not shine unto them.”&nbsp;
Pope Paul III, Council of Trent, Sess.
